# --- Memory Machine Exclusions ---

# Ignore heavy 3D model files (too big for GitHub)
*.3dm
*.3mb
*.gh
*.ghx

# Ignore temporary Rhino/Grasshopper backup files
*.tmp
*.bak
*.autosave
*.~*

# Ignore System & IDE junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Keep These (Safety Check) ---
!data/*.csv
!data/*.json
!logic/*.py
!*.html